com.hpl.mds.annotations.processor.parser

Class MethodParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hpl.mds.annotations.processor.parser.MethodParser

  • public class MethodParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Parses declared methods in a record schema in a generic way, including instance, abstract, static methods and constructors. The parsed information is returned in the form of a RecordInfo.MethodInfo
    Author:
    Abraham Alcantara
